3-db9a-a197-d7f71ff40000</guid></item><item><title>反对派在本格维尔议会抵制中击败了内塔尼亚胡政府的立法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-14/ty-article/.premium/opposition-defeats-netanyahu-govt-legislation-amid-ben-gvir-knesset-boycott/00000191-504d-d94f-adf1-d06f14450000</link><description>反对党领袖亚伊尔·拉皮德 (Yair Lapid) 表示，“如果你想知道政府是如何垮台的，那就像这样”；本-格维尔的政党抵制因其加入战时内阁的要求而进行的投票，迫使政府撤回当天议程上的所有法案</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 10:42:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-14/ty-article/.premium/opposition-defeats-netanyahu-govt-legislation-amid-ben-gvir-knesset-boycott/00000191-504d-d94f-adf1-d06f14450000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争意味着以色列也陷入围困</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/travel/2024-08-14/ty-article/.premium/the-gaza-war-means-that-israel-is-also-under-siege/00000191-5029-d140-a5ff-78eb68c10000</link><description>如今，在全国各地旅行几乎是不可能的，外国航空公司也抛弃了我们。但事实证明，总会有人想从你的困境中赚钱</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 10:31:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/travel/2024-08-14/ty-article/.premium/the-gaza-war-means-that-israel-is-also-under-siege/00000191-5029-d140-a5ff-78eb68c10000</guid></item><item><title>数百名以色列 10 月 7 日幸存者使用摇头丸接受创伤后应激障碍 (PTSD) 治疗</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-14/ty-article/.premium/hundreds-of-israeli-oct-7-survivors-to-undergo-ptsd-treatment-using-mdma/00000191-5011-dfc7-a7bd-fc5511200000</link><description>新星节大屠杀幸存者和士兵将参与一项结合个人和团体治疗的研究；一位顶级精神科医生表示，“我见过接受 MDMA 治疗的患者取得了标准治疗无法实现的进步”</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 09:48:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-14/ty-article/.premium/hundreds-of-israeli-oct-7-survivors-to-undergo-ptsd-treatment-using-mdma/00000191-5011-dfc7-a7bd-fc5511200000</guid></item><item><title>国防官员警告本-格维尔的圣殿山之行可能会增强哈马斯的力量，煽动以色列阿拉伯社会的骚乱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-14/ty-article/.premium/officials-warn-ben-gvir-temple-mount-visit-could-strengthen-hamas-in-israels-arab-society/00000191-4fb8-dfc7-a7bd-effd4e9d0000</link><description>以色列国防官员警告说，在本格维尔访问期间，以色列警方未能维持圣殿山/阿克萨建筑群的现状，可能会导致以色列的阿拉伯公民听从哈马斯和真主党的呼吁，与以色列人发生冲突</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 08:11:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-14/ty-article/.premium/officials-warn-ben-gvir-temple-mount-visit-could-strengthen-hamas-in-israels-arab-society/00000191-4fb8-dfc7-a7bd-effd4e9d0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡政府离摧毁以色列法治还有多远？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-14/ty-article/.premium/while-israel-is-at-war-netanyahu-and-his-allies-are-at-war-with-the-law/00000191-4ca6-d9b5-adbf-5ca7d36d0000</link><description>以色列总检察长持续面临被罢黜的威胁，部长和议会议员积极支持涉嫌战争罪的士兵，即使地区战争迫在眉睫，剥夺司法独立性和合法性的计划仍在全面实施。这个政府将不择手段</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 07:41:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-14/ty-article/.premium/while-israel-is-at-war-netanyahu-and-his-allies-are-at-war-with-the-law/00000191-4ca6-d9b5-adbf-5ca7d36d0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙协议或伊朗袭击：德黑兰在与以色列的紧张对峙中加大赌注</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-14/ty-article/.premium/hostage-deal-or-iranian-attack-tehran-ups-the-ante-in-tense-stand-off-with-israel/00000191-4cd7-d699-af95-4ef7040b0000</link><description>加沙停火协议与伊斯兰共和国对贝鲁特和德黑兰暗杀事件的反应之间的联系使得周四在多哈举行的峰会更加具有决定性。布林肯推迟访问该地区的决定表明了局势的紧张和不稳定</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 03:00:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-14/ty-article/.premium/hostage-deal-or-iranian-attack-tehran-ups-the-ante-in-tense-stand-off-with-israel/00000191-4cd7-d699-af95-4ef7040b0000</guid></item><item><title>努力评估国际刑事法院对内塔尼亚胡、Gallant的下一步行动，以色列推动推迟逮捕令</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-14/ty-article/.premium/israel-braces-as-icc-judges-review-request-for-arrest-warrants-against-netanyahu-gallant/00000191-4bd8-dff3-a5d3-4fd801be0000</link><description>当国际刑事法院法官审查以色列-巴勒斯坦冲突中的管辖权时，以色列官员仍然面临着悬而未决的问题。与此同时，检察官要求逮捕的三名哈马斯领导人中有两人最近被暗杀</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 03:00:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-14/ty-article/.premium/israel-braces-as-icc-judges-review-request-for-arrest-warrants-against-netanyahu-gallant/00000191-4bd8-dff3-a5d3-4fd801be0000</guid></item><item><title>美国、英国和德国驻以色列大使呼吁加沙停火、人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-14/ty-article-live/biden-expects-iran-wont-attack-israel-if-gaza-deal-reached-nyt-hamas-to-miss-talk/00000191-4eaf-d140-a5ff-7eef4bc30000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡在卡塔尔峰会前与人质协议谈判小组会面 ■ 五名巴勒斯坦人在以色列袭击和西岸袭击中丧生 ■ 美国驻贝鲁特特使表示，以色列与真主党的升级是可以避免的 ■ 两枚火箭落在以色列北部的什莫纳镇，没有发出警报；财产受损 ■ 14 人因极端正统派抗议以色列国防军征兵而被捕</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 02:31:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-14/ty-article-live/biden-expects-iran-wont-attack-israel-if-gaza-deal-reached-nyt-hamas-to-miss-talk/00000191-4eaf-d140-a5ff-7eef4bc30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列部门拒绝将女同性恋夫妇在孩子的出生证明上登记为“母亲”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-14/ty-article/.premium/israel-refusing-to-register-lesbian-couples-as-mothers-on-childrens-birth-certificate/00000191-4dba-d94f-adf1-ddfefb620000</link><description>内政部违反最高法院裁决，仍坚持写“父母和父母”</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 22:36:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-14/ty-article/.premium/israel-refusing-to-register-lesbian-couples-as-mothers-on-childrens-birth-certificate/00000191-4dba-d94f-adf1-ddfefb620000</guid></item><item><title>以色列城市重新考虑保护沿海悬崖免遭当地反对的计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-13/ty-article/.premium/israeli-city-rethinks-plan-to-protect-coastal-cliffs-from-crumbling-amid-local-opposition/00000191-4d11-d140-a5ff-7df354730000</link><description>由于海滩游客和水上运动爱好者的反对，以色列中部城市荷兹利亚正在重新考虑在其海岸修建防波堤的计划，他们表示该计划将影响附近海滩上的沙子堆积</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 20:28:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-13/ty-article/.premium/israeli-city-rethinks-plan-to-protect-coastal-cliffs-from-crumbling-amid-local-opposition/00000191-4d11-d140-a5ff-7df354730000</guid></item><item><title>中国和伊朗正在全面战争边缘地区建立第二条丝绸之路</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-13/ty-article/.premium/china-and-iran-are-establishing-a-second-silk-road-in-a-region-on-the-brink-of-all-out-war/00000191-4c81-d485-a1db-ff85a6130000</link><description>传统上，中国会乐于看到美国陷入另一场中东战争。但考虑到伊朗对中国在该地区的举措的重要性，美国知道这次情况并非如此。以色列有吗？</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 20:13:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-13/ty-article/.premium/china-and-iran-are-establishing-a-second-silk-road-in-a-region-on-the-brink-of-all-out-war/00000191-4c81-d485-a1db-ff85a6130000</guid></item><item><title>美国批准向以色列提供具有里程碑意义的价值200亿美元的武器包，其中包括价值180亿美元的F-15战斗机销售</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-13/ty-article/.premium/u-s-oks-landmark-20b-arms-package-to-israel-including-18b-f15-fighter-jets-sale/00000191-4d37-d699-af95-4ff7a4e80000</link><description>在国会最终成功通过拜登政府向以色列提供 140 亿美元紧急军事援助几个月后，这一宣布标志着美国历史上最重大的对以色列军售案之一</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 19:51:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-13/ty-article/.premium/u-s-oks-landmark-20b-arms-package-to-israel-including-18b-f15-fighter-jets-sale/00000191-4d37-d699-af95-4ff7a4e80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长告诉最高法院，迅速结束内塔尼亚胡的审判符合公众利益</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-13/ty-article/.premium/ag-to-top-court-public-interest-to-wrap-up-netanyahus-trial-quickly/00000191-4d11-dff3-a5d3-4f196ecd0000</link><description>司法部长加利·巴哈拉夫-米亚拉驳回了因战争而重新审查内塔尼亚胡利益冲突协议的请愿，但强调以色列总理必须避免做出涉及无关因素的决定，特别是涉及与战争有关的决定时</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 19:14:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-13/ty-article/.premium/ag-to-top-court-public-interest-to-wrap-up-netanyahus-trial-quickly/00000191-4d11-dff3-a5d3-4f196ecd0000</guid></item><item><title>“惊人的心理准备”：以色列运动员如何在巴黎奥运会上创造历史</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-08-13/ty-article-podcast/amazing-mental-preparation-how-israeli-athletes-made-history-at-the-paris-olympics/00000191-4c53-dae4-afd5-fff7dacd0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 17:18:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-08-13/ty-article-podcast/amazing-mental-preparation-how-israeli-athletes-made-history-at-the-paris-olympics/00000191-4c53-dae4-afd5-fff7dacd0000</guid></item><item><title>《国土报》调查：以色列军队利用巴勒斯坦平民检查加沙可能埋有诱杀装置的隧道</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/idf-uses-gazan-civilians-as-human-shields-to-inspect-potentially-booby-trapped-tunnels/00000191-4c84-d7fd-a7f5-7db6b99e0000</link><description>“我们的生命比他们的生命更重要”：几位消息人士称，没有涉嫌恐怖主义的加沙人被拘留，并在以色列国防军士兵进入之前被派往隧道和房屋中搜查隧道和房屋，以色列高级军官对此一无所知；以色列国防军声称这种做法是被禁止的</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 17:14:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/idf-uses-gazan-civilians-as-human-shields-to-inspect-potentially-booby-trapped-tunnels/00000191-4c84-d7fd-a7f5-7db6b99e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于战争状态，第 312 天：据报道以色列在停战谈判中表现出较小的灵活性</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-13/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-312-israel-reportedly-showing-less-flexibility-in-truce-talks/00000191-4c69-d9b5-adbf-5c6f808a0000</link><description>伊朗高级官员告诉路透社，只有加沙停火协议才能阻止伊朗直接攻击以色列 ■ 惠誉信用评级机构降低以色列评级，理由是担心加沙战争可能持续到 2025 年 ■ 据报道，伊朗担心以色列、美国可能会采取行动瞄准其核计划以应对袭击 ■ 据《纽约时报》报道，以色列在最近的停火谈判中表现出较小的灵活性 ■ 战争已过去 312 天，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 16:30:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-13/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-312-israel-reportedly-showing-less-flexibility-in-truce-talks/00000191-4c69-d9b5-adbf-5c6f808a0000</guid></item><item><title>外交部长表示，在伊朗威胁下，塞浦路斯已做好从以色列和黎巴嫩撤离的准备</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-08-13/ty-article/cyprus-ready-for-evacuees-from-israel-and-lebanon-foreign-minister-says-amid-iran-threat/00000191-4c0b-d695-a7b5-de0b3b720000</link><description>由于担心伊朗和真主党可能很快对以色列发动重大袭击，塞浦路斯表示，其从黎巴嫩和以色列撤离外国人的准备工作已经完成</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 14:39:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-08-13/ty-article/cyprus-ready-for-evacuees-from-israel-and-lebanon-foreign-minister-says-amid-iran-threat/00000191-4c0b-d695-a7b5-de0b3b720000</guid></item></channel></rss>